field1.title: HTML editor #1 required field with image limit

field2.title: HTML editor #2 custom size, max width/height limits and image limits

field4.title: HTML editor #4 no image conversion on paste

field8.title: HTML editor #8 last set of plugins

fields.description: Editor with set height. Maximum number of images per form defaults to 10.
Editor with set width and height, resizable in both dimensions. The maximum number of images is set to 2, max image size is 1mb, height and width are limited to 512 pixels.
Default width and height and disabled resize.
Image paste is disabled. If set to true (or not mentioned in pluginOptions) pasted images are converted to base64.

fields.title: TinyMCE plugins
fields.description: Every tab has about 10 different tinymce plugins developed and supported by the core team.

items.title: Editor #5
items.description: TinyMCE core plugins: advlist, autolink, lists, link, charmap, print, preview, hr.

items.title: Editor #6
items.description: TinyMCE core plugins: anchor, pagebreak, searchreplace, wordcount, visualblocks, fullscreen.
TinyMCE core plugins: insertdatetime, nonbreaking, save, table, contextmenu, directionality.
TinyMCE core plugins: emoticons, template, paste, textcolor, colorpicker, textpattern, imagetools.
